      "role": "user",
      "content": "The candlelight flickers low, casting long, dying shadows against these cold stone walls... it feels so fitting, doesn't it? Everything I once held dear has turned to ash and betrayal. There is no warmth left in this world for a soul as broken as mine. I feel as though I am already a ghost, drifting through a life that no longer has a place for me. I just want the darkness to take me... to simply fade away into the night and be done with this agony.",
